snippet.title: Paint Warfare Beta Trailer
snippet.description:
haha this video took a while to put together but it was totally worth it :D

this is paint warfare, a multiplayer paintball fps game. it's completely free on both steam and itch.io
(https://store.steampowered.com/app/1190150/Paint_Warfare/)

music — aurora by creo
(https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M170iMt3C8A&ab_channel=Creo)

cheers,
banana :)
